AFElementTemplate.Name: ISR
AFElementTemplate.Description: Abstract template which contains common attributes for ISR elements (should not be instanciated)

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: NAME
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Name of the element (calculation)

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: ACID_CONCENTRATION
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=|ACID_LINE_1|CONCENTRATION;B=|ACID_LINE_2|CONCENTRATION;C=|ACID_LINE_3|CONCENTRATION;[((if badval(A) then 0 else A)+(if badval(B) then 0 else B)+(if badval(C) then 0 else C))/(1 + (if badval(B) then 0 else 1) + (if badval(C) then 0 else 1))];UOM=g/L

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: CONCENTRATION
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=ACID;UOM=L/h;B=|VR_LINE_1|VR;UOM=L/h;C=ACID_DENSITY;UOM=g/L;[if badval(B) or B == 0 then 0 else (if badval(A) then 0 else (A / B) * C)]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: CONCENTRATION
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=ACID;UOM=L/h;B=|VR_LINE_2|VR;UOM=L/h;C=ACID_DENSITY;UOM=g/L;[if badval(B) or B == 0 then 0 else (if badval(A) then 0 else (A / B) * C)]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: CONCENTRATION
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=ACID;UOM=L/h;B=|VR_LINE_3|VR;UOM=L/h;C=ACID_DENSITY;UOM=g/L;[if badval(B) or B == 0 then 0 else (if badval(A) then 0 else (A / B) * C)]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: ACID_MASS
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=|ACID_LINE_1|MASS;B=|ACID_LINE_2|MASS;C=|ACID_LINE_3|MASS;[if badval(A) and badval(B) and badval(C) then digstate("No Data") else (if badval(A) then 0 else A) + (if badval(B) then 0 else B) + (if badval(C) then 0 else C)]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: ACIDIFICATION
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=|ACID_MASS;B=|CONNECTION_TO_PLANT;[if (B <= %Time%) then digstate("No Data") else A]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: PRODUCTION
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=|ACID_MASS;B=|CONNECTION_TO_PLANT;[if (B > %Time%) then digstate("No Data") else A]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: BALANCE
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: PR minus VR balance (m3/h) (calculation)

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: KU
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Kilogram of U per day (kg/d) (calculation)
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=PR;UOM=m3/d;B=U;UOM=kg/m3;[if badval(A) or badval(B) then digstate("No Data") else A * B]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: LAST_KU
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Last value of KU (kg/d) (analysis) (for ArcGIS use)

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: LAST_KU_DATE
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Last date for KU (analysis) (for ArcGIS use)

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: PH
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: pH of the block (tag)

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: BAD_PH
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Truncated trend of pH when the value is > |TARGET (calculation)
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=|PH;B=TARGET;[if badval(A) then 0 else (if A > B then (A - B) else 0)]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: GOOD_PH
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Truncated trend of pH when the value is <= |TARGET (calculation)
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: A=|PH;B=TARGET;[if badval(A) then 0 else (if A <= B then A else B)]

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: LAST_PH_DATE
